platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We’ve played plenty of grid-based puzzlers, but there’s just something about Link Twin that feels right. It might be the gorgeous, minimal art direction. Or maybe it's the wonderfully subtle animation or the excellent use of Force Touch. Whatever it is, we can’t stop swiping our way through the bite-sized challenges. Helping a duo reach different destinations is tough—but totally rewarding.
